---
layout: layout.njk
title: "SpelkBlog - Home"
---

<section class="hero">
  <p class="hero-statement">
    Technical solutions for problems that <em>Google doesn't have the answer to</em> — a personal notebook, publicly readable.
  </p>
  <div class="hero-meta">
    <strong>Focus</strong>
    Network Automation · Cisco · Python<br>
    APIs · HomeLab · Infrastructure
    <br><br>
    <strong>Status</strong>
    {{ collections.posts.length }} Solutions · Updated {{ collections.posts[0].date | date('%B %Y') }}
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-label"><span>Latest Solutions</span></div>

<table class="post-table">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>#</th>
      <th>Date</th>
      <th>Title</th>
      <th>Tag</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {% for post in collections.posts %}
    <tr onclick="window.location.href='{{ post.url }}'">
      <td class="num">{% if loop.index < 10 %}0{% endif %}{{ loop.index }}</td>
      <td class="date">{{ post.date | date('%d.%m.%y') }}</td>
      <td>
        <a class="title-link" href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
        <p class="desc">{{ post.templateContent | excerpt | safe }}</p>
        <p class="meta-inline">{{ post.templateContent | readingTime }} min read</p>
      </td>
      <td class="tag-cell"><span class="tag">Tech</span></td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
</table>

<div class="cta-block">
  <h3>Got a tech problem?</h3>
  <p>If you found a solution to something that's not covered here, or have a tech mystery that needs solving, let's connect!</p>
  <a href="/about/" class="cta-link">
    Get in Touch
    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
    </svg>
  </a>
</div>
